		help
		 comgt is a scripting language interpreter useful for establishing 
		  communications on serial lines and through PCMCIA modems as well as GPRS 
		  and 3G datacards.
		 http://www.pharscape.org/comgt.html
		 Felix Fietkau <nbd@openwrt.org>

