		tristate "kmod-video-gspca-zc3xx.............................. zc3xx webcam support"
		default y if DEFAULT_kmod-video-gspca-zc3xx
		default m if ALL
		depends on PACKAGE_kmod-video-gspca-core
		help
		 The ZC3XX USB Camera Driver (zc3xx) kernel module.
		 

